 secubox-core (>= 1.0),
 python3-uvicorn | python3-pip
Recommends: docker.io | podman, docker-compose | podman-compose, nginx
Description: SecuBox Jitsi Meet - Video Conferencing
 Docker-based Jitsi Meet video conferencing for SecuBox.
 Provides secure, scalable video meetings with screen sharing.
 .
 Features:
  - Full Jitsi Meet Docker stack (Web, Prosody, Jicofo, JVB)
  - JWT, LDAP, or internal authentication
  - Jibri recording and streaming support
  - SRTP/SRTCP encryption
  - Breakout rooms and lobby
  - CRT-light P31 phosphor theme dashboard
 .
 Ported from OpenWRT luci-app-jitsi concept.
 Provides FastAPI backend on /api/v1/jitsi/ via Unix socket.
